Express.js is a Node.js framework. It's the most popular framework as of now (the most starred on NPM).

ExpressJs is a web application framework that provides you with a simple API to build websites, web apps and back ends.

Plain Node.js is all about core modules.
In ExpressJs we create API's in less code than that of NodeJs.

Template engine pug,Mustache and Ejs which can use to add dynamic data on the website.
Changing the template directory of views directory